metadata.name: Carpe Diem
metadata.description:
Occasionally, the unexpected will happen, and a moment of magic occurs.

As sunrise was approaching, the clouds stayed heavy. And as time ticked on, they didnâ€™t dissipate. But at the last moment, minutes before daybreak, the blanketed sky opened slightly. And the sun peeked through a small window between 2 wisps,  illuminating the muted sky in golden color. I seized my opportunity.
